      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-service-sector-contracts-april-price-pressures-reaccelerate-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美國服務業在3月出現萎縮，而企業為投入支付的價格指標則大幅上漲，這是通膨前景令人擔憂的跡象。]]></description>
